        "tags": [
          "保质期",
          "换算规则"
        ],
        "link": "https://school.jinritemai.com/doudian/web/article/aJk964FFQKKZ",
        "body": "<ul><li>保质期指在既定贮存环境下保持品质的期限。</li><li>保质期以月计，按<span class=\"num\">1个月=30天</span>换算；以年计，按<span class=\"num\">1年=365天</span>换算。</li><li>临期天数计算向上取整。</li></ul>"
      },
      {
        "cardId": "shelf:1",
        "sourceId": "dy-rule-aJk964FFQKKZ",
        "title": "临期商品标注与展示要求",
        "severity": "critical",
        "severityText": "强制",
        "date": "2026-05-26",
        "tags": [
          "临期标注",
          "展示要求"
        ],
        "link": "https://school.jinritemai.com/doudian/web/article/aJk964FFQKKZ",
        "body": "<ul><li>临期商品须在标题写明“临期商品”字样。</li><li>详情页最上方显著标示“此商品为临近保质期商品”。</li><li>临期起算时间以商家发货后物流系统揽收时间为准。</li></ul>"
      },
      {
        "cardId": "shelf:2",
        "sourceId": "dy-rule-aJk964FFQKKZ",
        "title": "临期商品分级标准（按保质期）",
        "severity": "warning",
        "severityText": "警告",
        "date": "2026-05-26",
        "tags": [
          "临期天数",
          "分级标准"
        ],
        "link": "https://school.jinritemai.com/doudian/web/article/aJk964FFQKKZ",
        "body": "<ul><li>保质期≥365天：剩余≤<span class=\"num\">45天</span>为临期。</li><li>180天≤保质期<365天：剩余≤<span class=\"num\">30天</span>为临期。</li><li>90天≤保质期<180天：剩余≤<span class=\"num\">20天</span>为临期。</li><li>30天≤保质期<90天：剩余≤<span class=\"num\">10天</span>为临期。</li><li>15天≤保质期<30天：剩余≤<span class=\"num\">5天</span>为临期。</li><li>保质期<15天：剩余≤<span class=\"num\">4天</span>为临期。</li></ul>"
      },
      {
        "cardId": "shelf:3",
